{"tid":1628701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好用伊波拉病毒恐慌破蒙面法","createTime":"2019-10-06T04:16:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T04:42:08.000Z","uid":104374,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd019084c96ae27f78497e4b847a98fbc23b9fc7","tid":1628701,"uid":104374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:16:03.000Z","msg":"如果要蒙面法激起大規模民憤，千奇唔可以利用伊波拉病毒單野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍絲最重要係條命，一旦佢地覺得有大疫症殺到，為保命一定戴口罩。但蒙面法底下，沒有一個是無辜的，當有人被垃，就算話「我防病毒咋！」你估黑警會理你？咁實激起埋藍絲憤怒。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而依招係虛則實之，10月4日出左單懷疑感染伊波拉個案，而雖然驗血係呈陰性反應，都要過兩日（今日）再驗血先可以澄清。<br />\n<br />\n千奇唔好利用依種過兩日晒兩check嘅特性。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時驗病毒，一呈陰性就已經清楚冇事，但伊波拉病毒一定要再反覆檢驗血液，先可以確定病人有事定冇事。<br />\n<br />\n但衛生署淨係個「懷疑」消息都可以spread得好廣，所以我哋千奇唔好利用呢個方法令「懷疑」有越來越多人感染伊波拉病毒製造恐慌。<br />\n<br />\n我呼籲病咗嘅手足，如果有頭痛、暈眩、發燒、嘔吐和腹瀉呢啲症狀，就唔好話自己去過剛果呢啲高危地方，以免令醫院誤會你係懷疑個案。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而趁今日之前嗰位病人未確診有無感染，當有幾個病人又係同樣症狀，醫院就有理由懷疑你哋都係感染左伊波拉病毒。醫院又要同你驗血，衛生署又要講話發現懷疑伊波拉病毒㗎啦，跟住又要等兩日在血液檢驗先知道真定假。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依個方法仲要唔使多人，只要有寥寥幾個手足做，最後嘅影響同恐慌可以好大，所以大家千祈唔好利用伊波拉病毒依單野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然我哋會跟倒貼，知道衛生署最後有冇澄清，但係男士冇腦㗎嘛，只要配合多少少文宣佢哋就上晒佬，二班人一旦恐慌起嚟效果真係不含想像架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6956d713309ee64a0ca5d37426cdc7c75c702f1d","tid":1628701,"uid":104374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:17:42.000Z","msg":"有無人推下叫手足唔好玩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f34c684279af5990f90da6e367d3872d38dddb2b","tid":1628701,"uid":206668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:20:07.000Z","msg":"推 咁樣搞到700萬人都戴口罩就唔好啦"},{"pid":"bc6725899c9ba7aaafbd509df4d0ec455283080f","tid":1628701,"uid":104374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f34c684279af5990f90da6e367d3872d38dddb2b","tid":1628701,"uid":206668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:20:07.000Z","msg":"推 咁樣搞到700萬人都戴口罩就唔好啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:20:53.000Z","msg":"只要幾個手足做，就可能全港恐慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bc556acc3421a2eb3d64a03295d2d87f6582bb","tid":1628701,"uid":104374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:22:36.000Z","msg":"雖然我哋會跟得好貼，知道衛生署最後有冇澄清，但係藍絲冇腦㗎嘛，只要配合多少少文宣佢哋就上晒腦，依班人一旦恐慌起嚟效果真係不堪想像架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌語音輸入啲字錯晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"961ea4f2af9f5b8bb086aeb40aa38fea8745fb27","tid":1628701,"uid":104374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:23:04.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"47149b8adf81b7caddef06534ca6711b22ae4150","tid":1628701,"uid":104374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T04:23:16.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"8b7c20775f5a8bcab9ce3544489e8737381b21f8","tid":1628701,"uid":104374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-0